headline: Dow Recognized With Six Wins in the 2025 Big Innovation Awards
summary: For the 9th consecutive year, Dow (NYSE:DOW) has been recognized for innovation by the Business Intelligence Group (BIG). In the 2025 BIG Innovation Awards, Dow technologies won six awards in the Transformative Products category-more than any other ...
